      <p>Technical resume writing requires a fundamentally different approach than business resume writing. Software engineers, data professionals, and product managers have rich, complex experience that generic resume writers cannot translate into the language hiring managers use to evaluate technical candidates.</p>
      <p>Askia specializes in technical resume writing for engineers, data scientists, product managers, DevOps engineers, AI/ML engineers, and engineering managers — from IC through Staff and Principal level, and through the IC-to-manager transition.</p>
