<section class="section">
  <div class="container faq-stage">
    <div class="faq-header">
      <p class="hero-eyebrow">Common Questions</p>
      <h2 class="section-title section-title-glow">Professional resume writing — what to know</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-grid">
      <div class="faq-card">
        <h3>How much does a professional resume writing service cost?</h3>
        <p>Askia offers resume writing as part of tiered coaching packages. The investment depends on the scope of support needed — resume only, resume plus LinkedIn, or full coaching including interview prep and offer strategy. Book a free strategy call for current pricing and the right package for your situation.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-card">
        <h3>How long does resume writing take?</h3>
        <p>The core resume rewrite is typically completed over one to two focused sessions. Most clients have a working draft within 48–72 hours of the first session, with revisions completed within a week.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-card">
        <h3>Do I need to provide my old resume or can you build from scratch?</h3>
        <p>Both work. If you have an existing resume, we use it as a starting point and rebuild from there. If you are starting from scratch (first professional resume, major career change), we build from a structured intake about your experience, accomplishments, and target roles.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-card">
        <h3>Will my resume pass ATS?</h3>
        <p>Yes. All resumes written through Askia are ATS-compatible — clean formatting, proper section headers, keyword-optimized content, and no elements (graphics, tables, text boxes) that cause parsing failures in major applicant tracking systems.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-card">
        <h3>What is better — a resume writing service or career coaching?</h3>
        <p>The resume is one component of a job search. If your only bottleneck is resume quality, resume writing alone may be sufficient. If you are not getting responses despite applying, or you are getting interviews but not offers, the bottleneck is probably bigger than the resume. Full career coaching addresses resume, LinkedIn, interview prep, and offer strategy as an integrated system.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-card">
        <h3>Can you write a resume for any industry?</h3>
        <p>Askia specializes in tech, business, finance, operations, sales, marketing, healthcare administration, and legal/compliance — industries where we have deep hiring-side knowledge of what moves candidates forward at the $100K–$350K level.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

